{"tid":1462983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（旅客問題）機場活動緊急建議","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:25:53.000Z","uid":200062,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"277720c832a948cdf90a72a503cca9a052649fe0","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"1 對旅客倍加禮貌<br />\n2 唔好嚇親人 有報導話嚇到人喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3 可以就旅客受到影響致歉 不過一定要解釋動機原因 同堅持我地做緊正確嘅事<br />\n4 向旅客提供各類資訊 eg交易、住宿等<br />\n5 向旅客提供食水、小食<br />\n6 人道原因要放人行 報導話今日唔比個心臟有事嘅澳洲人過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96edc7dd674ce5e35bf0841ad137c1e3fb36748","tid":1462983,"uid":257422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"借post:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ 談社運正當性 ] 塞鐵阻人返工可以係因為依個香港佢地有份；亦解釋到點解唔好塞離境旅客~</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462734</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿我唔係講策略/效果既問題。<br />\n<br />\n無疑塞鐵/罷工會惹人反感，唔應該日日做。<br />\n<br />\n但亦無可否認既，就係依類不合作運動係有佢既道德正當性係入面，因為返工既人多數都係香港社會既一份子，而佢地係有責任去維護香港人既人權自由；所以你阻佢，就算對社運進程無好處都好，你都係出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相對地，離境旅客有好多都唔係香港既持份者，基本上佢地係無任何責任為我地既人權自由付出任何代價；最簡單既理解方法，就係我相信你自己都唔會認為自己對其他國家既人權自由有絕對既責任，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n所以，離境旅客係搞不得。<br />\n<br />\n但，我地有權去機場、有權係唔阻其他旅客既情況下坐地下，所以靠人多去令機場function唔到，責任就唔係我地度，剛剛星期一既塞爆機場亦係絕對無問題。"},{"pid":"1002a264753f03e733aa04e24b1631ab17afc471","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f3df399d753ce7b44b59d6a805dda574a2224126","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 818"},{"pid":"f8fc646aac6f2f8caec267150ef3b16161452981","tid":1462983,"uid":69145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85cf98038084ccdc403c306a342ad30cd8fd71fb","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:47.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"e7f1fe9c0cffe2409532fcf2986dc644299f53ef","tid":1462983,"uid":285371,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"阻旅客上機<br />\n外國人番到hometown 會話班示威者搞事<br />\n佢上唔到機而班機無取消 <br />\n<br />\n你和平集會 人多塞路<br />\n機場自然會cancel 班機<br />\n班旅客屌政府多過示威者<br />\n<br />\n一開始去機場集會既意義<br />\n係向國際宣傳我地被政府迫害<br />\n狗行使武力<br />\n唔夠人塞就做文宣唔洗急<br />\n<br />\n手足入緊黎啦<br />\n不割蓆 不分化"},{"pid":"eef9c70c7ba9d2a3d7213d926f73c9e2452276b1","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"892796c58fe9ff2392338ab87dde4dc3e7414ba8","tid":1462983,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"應該以暫停所有航班但容許國泰系航班有限度復飛為持續抗爭手段<br />\n<br />\nI strongly recommend the upcoming campaign to bar all flights from operating from/to Hong Kong with the exception of flights operated by Cathay Pacific Group but at a reduced throughput!!!"},{"pid":"ae83dc17f18ba162555b8456566936e789c3257a","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"3836a94557ab55c178287a88ef6ef0cfb8d9e7d7","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"c3daf3dbb96f05a77b1aee3dc05f0390e4df85cd","tid":1462983,"uid":74155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"蝦條照呃，但事後要冧返掂條女！"},{"pid":"5134808c7d79713f5c7bb56ce78605668aaadb2b","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite