,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"但無啦啦比人屌 用d好難聽既說話鬧 好難忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2c97485102180360c71de352271aca54a45cdc","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25ceca5d539626dee4addd0d4d21aa8d4513f8f","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9a998f3dd2e5db99c44bf7134016775329083df","tid":1462983,"uid":179738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"但無啦啦比人屌 用d好難聽既說話鬧 好難忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:59:41.000Z","msg":"忍一時之氣"},{"pid":"cd54d33c323dff8f0915cc6542c433a6f030a916","tid":1462983,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:59:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>其實由頭到尾都唔係為左癱瘓機場<br />\n應該係「機場和你飛 文宣活動」<br />\n活動無論人數多少都係叫口號 靜坐 遊行<br />\n只不過人數要非常多 多到佢癱瘓</strong></span>"},{"pid":"32a2ef841e73f9c880e913443def624e39893c1b","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c57d14e8f85bf181530aa93db1109f0e057200","tid":1462983,"uid":200062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207ea01e1c9e6d13ec365867a15f12580fb24970","tid":1462983,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"919b157d8a1d521bb3e76ef65eda2faaf1639950","tid":1462983,"uid":254213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a96edc7dd674ce5e35bf0841ad137c1e3fb36748","tid":1462983,"uid":257422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"借post:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ 談社運正當性 ] 塞鐵阻人返工可以係因為依個香港佢地有份；亦解釋到點解唔好塞離境旅客~</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462734</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿我唔係講策略/效果既問題。<br />\n<br />\n無疑塞鐵/罷工會惹人反感，唔應該日日做。<br />\n<br />\n但亦無可否認既，就係依類不合作運動係有佢既道德正當性係入面，因為返工既人多數都係香港社會既一份子，而佢地係有責任去維護香港人既人權自由；所以你阻佢，就算對社運進程無好處都好，你都係出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相對地，離境旅客有好多都唔係香港既持份者，基本上佢地係無任何責任為我地既人權自由付出任何代價；最簡單既理解方法，就係我相信你自己都唔會認為自己對其他國家既人權自由有絕對既責任，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n所以，離境旅客係搞不得。<br />\n<br />\n但，我地有權去機場、有權係唔阻其他旅客既情況下坐地下，所以靠人多去令機場function唔到，責任就唔係我地度，剛剛星期一既塞爆機場亦係絕對無問題。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佔機場既目的係為咗d咩事 你連個目的都錯<br />\n<br />\n佔機場係要影響香港經濟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人多當然可以阻到 但人少就要變通喇<br />\n只佔唔阻 你係幫機場商店 港鐵 增加佢地生意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:00:09.000Z","msg":"師兄姐係你覺得只要達到目的就咩方法都應該做？<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪出埋&quot;魔法&quot;搞機場都係正確策略？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用下個腦，一件事可以有好多層面咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810493a5d0ae6b55f4ef1cd07d11531bbf4f6951","tid":1462983,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/BrTVRxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBrTVRxG.png&h=8cfc6754&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c12d2fbed9c7eb21d6c86f7c3a718c1c4132b1aa","tid":1462983,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f